        {
            "id": 6009027,
            "title": "歐洲央行再降息1碼 助經濟抵禦關稅壓力",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>歐洲央行 (ECB) 周四 (5 日) 如期降息 1 碼(25 個基點)，將存款便利利率下調至 2%，低於 2023 年年中曾創下的 4% 高點。歐洲央行此舉正值<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>區經濟面臨高度不確定性的時刻。企業和決策者都在關注全球局勢升溫所帶來的挑戰，尤其是美國總統川普的關稅政策，市場普遍認為這將對經濟成長帶來重大壓力。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009027%2Fl%2F93bcb4aa8a1fe05e0aaf1d7b6ce2d254.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">歐洲央行再降息1碼 助經濟抵禦關稅壓力(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此次降息後，歐洲央行存款利率 (Deposit Facility Rate)─即關鍵利率─降至 2.0%，主要再融資利率 (Main Refinancing Rate) 降至 2.15%、邊際貸款利率 (Marginal Lending Rate) 降至 2.4%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>至於關稅對通膨的影響，目前看來並不明朗。決策者表示，這將取決於歐盟是否以及如何採取反制措施。目前歐盟方面的報復性措施仍暫緩，但歐盟領袖已表示，一旦有需要，將準備好祭出對等關稅。此外，歐洲各國計畫大幅增加國防支出，這對經濟的影響仍存在變數。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據本周稍早公布的初步數據，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>區通膨率已降至 1.9%，低於歐洲央行 2% 的目標水準。儘管利率趨於寬鬆，經濟成長依然疲弱。最新預估顯示，今年第一季<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>區經濟僅成長 0.3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>持續更新...</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
